{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Roll 1D10 or choose a category below for each distinctive feature your character has. You can choose the same category multiple times. Then choose a feature or features from the entry. These are all cosmetic and do not affect game values, but it is useful to keep your character\u8217's characteristics and skills in mind when picking distinctive features.\par}
