{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Fury (1):} Enrages target, speeding their attacks.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Inescapable Bonds (3):} Immobilizes target, requires a resistance roll.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Liken Shape (4):} Assume the image of another person.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Muddle (1):} Disorients target.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Pox (1):} Reduces target\u8217's power points, requires a resistance roll.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel3 \b \fs24 Occult Spells\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Brazier of Power (4):} Creates a reservoir of power points.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Chain of Being (4):} Creates a pool of power points.\par}
