{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel3 \b \fs24 Summoning Spells\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Summon Demon (1):} Summons a demon.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Summon Elemental (1):} Summons an elemental.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel3 \b \fs24 Utility Spells\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Bird\u8217's Vision (1):} Controls a bird and sees through its eyes.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Breath of Life (1):} Provides breathable air underwater or elsewhere.\par}
