{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Riot Gear:} A heavy bulletproof jacket and toughened clothing coverall, with plates in strategic body parts and a helmet.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Scale:} Scale armor (sometimes called scale mail) consists of overlapping metal scales of various shapes and sizes fastened onto a backing.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Splint:} See the description for lamellar.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Studded:} See the description for lamellar.\par}
