{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Great Sword (used one-handed) 150%, 2D8+dm (bleeding) +2D6 flame (special)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Whip 90%, 1D3\u8211-1+\u189 ?dm (entangle) +1D6 fire (special)\par}
